00:42:59,210 --> 00:43:00,640
The rebellion has been quelled.

810
00:43:00,640 --> 00:43:02,060
Ming is being held in custody by me,

811
00:43:02,060 --> 00:43:03,320
awaiting your orders.

812
00:43:08,980 --> 00:43:10,040
I'll order someone

813
00:43:10,250 --> 00:43:12,450
to remove these barricades right away.

814
00:43:26,810 --> 00:43:28,010
Keep them as they are.

815
00:43:29,170 --> 00:43:32,440
Everything has its cause and effect.

816
00:43:33,050 --> 00:43:34,780
I have some responsibility for

817
00:43:35,690 --> 00:43:37,900
the way Ming turned out.

818
00:43:40,870 --> 00:43:41,950
Shuang.

819
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:46,480
Send him back home.

820
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:54,020
He and I, father and son, will
never see each other again.

821
00:43:57,330 --> 00:43:58,000
Father!

822
00:44:12,910 --> 00:44:14,760
Is Master Xishan alright?

823
00:44:16,420 --> 00:44:18,860
Father is unwell after this incident.

824
00:44:19,330 --> 00:44:22,210
He can't see you this time.

825
00:44:24,750 --> 00:44:26,010
But he told me

826
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:27,440
to thank you

827
00:44:27,610 --> 00:44:30,510
for your assistance to the
Liufeng family this time.

828
00:44:30,510 --> 00:44:32,640
There's no need for thanks between us.

829
00:44:35,130 --> 00:44:37,100
You were willing to go against
the wishes of your clan elders

830
00:44:37,100 --> 00:44:39,410
to lead your troops and help me
quell this rebellion.

831
00:44:39,410 --> 00:44:40,390
Our Liufeng family

832
00:44:40,390 --> 00:44:42,630
will definitely remember this kindness.

833
00:44:42,630 --> 00:44:43,510
No matter when,

834
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:45,100
I will never turn a blind eye

835
00:44:45,100 --> 00:44:46,770
to your matters.

